{"tid":665420,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[歐洲jj]  Basel/ Colmar 附近有咩地方好去","createTime":"2018-05-15T02:34:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T00:01:02.000Z","uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e67ef3cb93d795cb97efdb7c01c4da44d3cd3ced","tid":665420,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T02:34:17.000Z","msg":"六月會去兩日colmar <br />\n諗住basel 入&amp;走<br />\n搵咗好耐資料但附近景點好似冇咩地方好去<br />\n瑞士我去過zurich geneva interlaken grindelwald zermatt bern jungfrau lucerne st moritz Schaffhausen<br />\n唔想重覆<br />\n有咩地方值得去又唔太遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5cbf82fa5a6e89d95e18ccc3037f2deba29ea1d","tid":665420,"uid":18947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T02:52:09.000Z","msg":"Basel個日不幸星期日去，咩都無開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟住行左陣就返上去德國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我記得好似有座紅色樓幾特別，唔係好記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6036b3c006195aebeabdd3dce747c3ea09fea57","tid":665420,"uid":10189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T03:09:15.000Z","msg":"有個Laufenburg係瑞德邊界<br />\n去既話可以坐德國bahn車去(Basel德國月台)<br />\n比瑞士車平兩歐左右(瑞士車係市中心)<br />\n<br />\nBasel真係無咩好做<br />\n想平既就坐輕軌去德國嗰邊食飯<br />\n平唔少"},{"pid":"6d580a4d48f8826cb4634345664c70b0d5719368","tid":665420,"uid":42328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T08:49:39.000Z","msg":"Freiburg <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有一日既話可以去埋titisee (黑森林) 食舊黑森林蛋糕"},{"pid":"e8e6479e5956f7c746b62ec710cfa974b29dca92","tid":665420,"uid":141782,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6d580a4d48f8826cb4634345664c70b0d5719368","tid